an class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">                &lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk7\">li</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">            &lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk7\">ul</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">        &lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk7\">div</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    &lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk7\">main</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>Şimdi \"img\" içindeki yola uygun biçimde bir resim ekleyelim.”template” in bulunduğu dosyaya “images” dosyası açıyoruz. İçine herhangi bir resim sürükleyip bırakıyoruz. Sonra sağ tıklayıp “rename” e basıp buradaki ismi veriyoruz ki resmi bulabilsin. Kısa isimler verirseniz işiniz daha kolay olur. Bu işlemden sonra artık resmi sayfamızda görebiliriz. Ve alt kısmında ürün ismi markası ve fiyatı da görünüyor. Fakat resim kendi büyüklüğünde ve şu anki görünüm korkunç :D. Şimdi bu görünümü düzenlemeye başlayalım. </p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container monokai\" data-language=\"css\" data-index=\"1\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk5\">.products</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk9 mtki\">display</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: </span><span class=\"mtk9\">flex</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk9 mtki\">justify-content</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: </span><span class=\"mtk9\">center</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk9 mtki\">align-items</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: </span><span class=\"mtk9\">center</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">}</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk5\">.products</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk7\">li</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk9 mtki\">flex</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: </span><span class=\"mtk4\">0</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk4\">1</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk4\">25</span><span class=\"mtk7\">rem</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk9 mtki\">margin</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: </span><span class=\"mtk4\">1</span><span class=\"mtk7\">rem</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk9 mtki\">height</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: </span><span class=\"mtk4\">50</span><span class=\"mtk7\">rem</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk9 mtki\">border-bottom</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: </span><span class=\"mtk4\">.1</span><span class=\"mtk7\">rem</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk9\">rgb</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk4\">216</span><span class=\"mtk1\">, </span><span class=\"mtk4\">216</span><span class=\"mtk1\">, </span><span class=\"mtk4\">216</span><span class=\"mtk1\">) </span><span class=\"mtk9\">solid</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk9 mtki\">list-style-type</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: </span><span class=\"mtk9\">none</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">}</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk5\">.product-image</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk9 mtki\">max-width</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: </span><span class=\"mtk4\">34</span><span class=\"mtk7\">rem</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk9 mtki\">max-height</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: </span><span class=\"mtk4\">34</span><span class=\"mtk7\">rem</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">}</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>Önceliğimiz tüm ürünlerin ortalanması. Bunun için de flex ayarlamalarını yapıyoruz. “justify-content” ve “align-items”e center içeriğimizi ortalar.\nİkinci olarak ürünler içindeki tüm \"li\" lere stil veriyoruz. “flex” özelliğinde görüldüğü üzere 3 seçenek oluşturuyoruz. Birincisi \"flex-grow\" : Esnek bir ürünün gerektiğinde büyüme yeteneğini tanımlar. İkincisi ise \"flex-shrink\" satırda yeterli alan olmadığında esnek ürünün diğer esnek öğelere göre ne kadar küçüleceğini ayarlar. Üçüncü seçenek \"flex-basis\": esnek öğenin başlangıç boyutunu belirtir. Bu seçenekleri eğer istersek ayrı ayrı da tanımlayabiliriz.\nBorder ve yükseklik istediğimiz gibi ayarlıyoruz. İstenmeyen liste stilinden kurtulmak için “list-style-type: none” ekliyoruz. Son olarak resme de maksimum ulaşabileceği büyüklüğü tanımlıyoruz. </p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container monokai\" data-language=\"html\" data-index=\"2\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    &lt;</span><span class=\"mtk7\">div</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk5\">class</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk6\">&quot;product-name&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">        &lt;</span><span class=\"mtk7\">a</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk5\">href</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk6\">&quot;product.html&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;Kazak&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk7\">a</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    &lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk7\">div</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>Şimdi diğer ürün seçeneklerine bakalım. Öncelikle ürün ismini yukarıdaki gibi \"a\" tagi ile saralım ki bizi bir yerlere götürebilsin. Tanımladığımız yol ise şimdilik yok. Stil verme işlemiyle devam ediyoruz.</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container monokai\" data-language=\"css\" data-index=\"3\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk5\">.product-name</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk9 mtki\">font-size</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: </span><span class=\"mtk4\">2</span><span class=\"mtk7\">rem</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">}</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk7\">a</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk9 mtki\">text-decoration</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: </span><span class=\"mtk9\">none</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk9 mtki\">color</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: </span><span class=\"mtk9\">black</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">}</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk5\">.product-brand</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk9 mtki\">font-size</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: </span><span class=\"mtk4\">1.5</span><span class=\"mtk7\">rem</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk9 mtki\">color</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: </span><span class=\"mtk4\">#a3a3a3</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">}</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk5\">.product-price</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk9 mtki\">font-size</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: